<s> I work on the berlin project: http://www.berlin-consortium.org  </s>
<s> We use CORBA, and I have written an API in OMG IDL for storing attributed text etc. - similar to the DOM spec., except DOM looks more powerful.  </s>
<s> We intend to use DOM instead.  </s>
<s> Berlin is GPL'ed, so I have two questions: 1) Is it legal for us to implement DOM and distribute it under GPL/LGPL?  </s>
<s> 2) Is it legal for us to put the DOM IDL-files in our cvs repository, and just compile everything with berlin, and distribute it all under GPL/LGPL?  </s>
<s> We intend to write text-widgets that use the DOM API as part of Berlin.  </s>
<s> So your DOM editor could easily be implemented in Berlin, when our GUI-stuff is ready for it.  </s>
